  "readme": "# table\n\n---\n\n通用表格组件，可带表头表尾，用于显示各类数据。\n\n---\n\n## 演示文档\n\n<link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"screen\" href=\"src/table.css\">\n\n### 正常表格\n\n````html\n<div class=\"ui-table-container\">\n    <table class=\"ui-table\"><!-- 可以在class中加入ui-table-inbox或ui-table-noborder分别适应不同的情况 -->\n        <thead>\n            <tr>\n                <th>创建时间</th>\n                <th>名称<em class=\"ft-bar\">|</em>交易号</th>\n                <th>对方</th>\n                <th>金额<em class=\"ft-bar\">|</em>明细</th>\n                <th>状态</th>\n                <th>操作</th>\n                <th>备注</th>\n            </tr>\n        </thead><!-- 表头可选 -->\n        <tbody>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"ui-table-split\">\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"ui-table-split\">\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n            </tr>\n        </tbody>\n        <tfoot>\n            <tr>\n                <td colspan=\"7\">表尾数据</td>\n            </tr>\n        </tfoot><!-- 表尾可选 -->\n    </table>\n</div>\n````\n\n### 无边框的表格\n\n````html\n<table class=\"ui-table ui-table-noborder\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>1</td>\n            <td>吴实</td>\n            <td>\n                <p>电话：13000111222</p>\n                <p>地址：浙江省杭州市西湖区晚唐路567号</p>\n            </td>\n            <td>操作</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr class=\"ui-table-split\">\n            <td>2</td>\n            <td>吴实</td>\n            <td>\n                <p>电话：13000111222</p>\n                <p>地址：浙江省杭州市西湖区晚唐路567号</p>\n            </td>\n            <td>操作</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>3</td>\n            <td>吴实</td>\n            <td>\n                <p>电话：13000111222</p>\n                <p>地址：浙江省杭州市西湖区晚唐路567号</p>\n            </td>\n            <td>操作</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr class=\"ui-table-split\">\n            <td>4</td>\n            <td>吴实</td>\n            <td>\n                <p>电话：13000111222</p>\n                <p>地址：浙江省杭州市西湖区晚唐路567号</p>\n            </td>\n            <td>操作</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n````\n\n### 可以嵌在别的框里的表格\n\n````html\n<div class=\"ui-table-container\">\n    <table class=\"ui-table ui-table-inbox\"><!-- 可以在class中加入ui-table-inbox或ui-table-noborder分别适应不同的情况 -->\n        <thead>\n            <tr>\n                <th>创建时间</th>\n                <th>名称<em class=\"ft-bar\">|</em>交易号</th>\n                <th>对方</th>\n                <th>金额<em class=\"ft-bar\">|</em>明细</th>\n                <th>状态</th>\n                <th>操作</th>\n                <th>备注</th>\n            </tr>\n        </thead><!-- 表头可选 -->\n        <tbody>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td class=\"ui-table-action\">Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"ui-table-split\">\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n                <td class=\"ui-table-action\">Data</td>\n                <td>Data</td>\n            </tr>\n        </tbody>\n    </table>\n</div>\n````\n\n### 固定布局（不按表格内容设定列宽）\n\n> .ui-table-layout-fixed\n\n````html\n<table class=\"ui-table ui-table-layout-fixed\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th width=\"10%\">创建时间</th>\n            <th width=\"20%\">名称<em class=\"ft-bar\">|</em>交易号</th>\n            <th width=\"20%\">对方</th>\n            <th width=\"10%\">金额<em class=\"ft-bar\">|</em>明细</th>\n            <th width=\"10%\">状态</th>\n            <th width=\"20%\">操作</th>\n            <th width=\"10%\">备注</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>looooooooooooooooooong data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n````\n\n非固定布局第一列就被撑宽了。\n\n````html\n<table class=\"ui-table\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th width=\"10%\">创建时间</th>\n            <th width=\"20%\">名称<em class=\"ft-bar\">|</em>交易号</th>\n            <th width=\"20%\">对方</th>\n            <th width=\"10%\">金额<em class=\"ft-bar\">|</em>明细</th>\n            <th width=\"10%\">状态</th>\n            <th width=\"20%\">操作</th>\n            <th width=\"10%\">备注</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>looooooooooooooooooong data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n            <td>Data</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n````\n",
